{"lemma":"شَوْبُ","slug":"شَوْبُ","root":"ش.#.ب","root_slug":"ش-_-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ش-_-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"شَوْب","root":"شوب","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":7},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["","n23257","n23258"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B4%D9%8E%D9%88%D9%92%D8%A8%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of شَابَ (šāba) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"mixture, blend"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"vitiation, flaw"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"roiling, heat attacking from the outside"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"hot wind, simoom"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to ward off"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to heat up at the outside, to tan"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Of the root ش و ب (š w b). See it for more."},"ipa":["/ʃawb/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n23257","headword_ar":"شَوْبٌ","root":"$wb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"inf. n. of 1 [q. v.]. (S, A, &c.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA $awoba walaA rawoba","text_ar":"لَا شَوْبَ وَلَا رَوْبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", occurring in a trad., means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There is,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shall be, no dishonesty, insincerity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dissimulation, nor mixing, in the selling,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"buying:"},{"kind":"text","text":"so says IAar: or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I am irresponsible with respect to this commodity:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, as he is related to have said,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thou art irresponsible for its being"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"faulty,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"defective."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA. [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$awobapN","text_ar":"شَوْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$awobN","text_ar":"شَوْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iyaAbN","text_ar":"شِيَابٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, TA,) [each an inf. n. used as a subst. properly so termed,] or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iyaAbapN","text_ar":"شِيَابَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (so in one copy of the S,) signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A mixture; an admixture;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing mixed with another thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA.) Thus"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$awobFA","text_ar":"شَوْبًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies in the Kur xxxvii. 65: (TA:) or, accord. to one reading, the word there is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uwbFA","text_ar":"شُوبًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing with which another thing is mixed."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$~awobu","text_ar":"الشَّوْبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies [particularly]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What is mixed"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with something else"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of water"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of milk:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saqaAhu Al*~awoba biAl$~awobi","text_ar":"سَقَاهُ الذَّوْبَ بِالشَّوْبِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He gave him to drink honey with water,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"milk, mixed"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"therewith"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saqaAhu Al$~awoba biAl*~awobi","text_ar":"سَقَاهُ الشَّوْبَ بِالذَّوْبِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He gave him to drink milk"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mixed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with honey."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IDrd, TA.) And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Mixed honey;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA EinodiY","text_ar":"مَا عِنْدِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$awobN walaA rawobN","text_ar":"شَوْبٌ وَلَا رَوْبٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I have not mixed honey nor milk such as is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAy^ib","text_ar":"رَايِب"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]: (IAar, TA:) or [simply]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"honey"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.; (A, Msb, TA;) so called because they mix it with beverages; (Msb;) as in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saqaAhu Al$~awoba biAlr~awobi","text_ar":"سَقَاهُ الشَّوْبَ بِالرَّوْبِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He gave him to drink honey with clarified butter,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with milk."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Broth;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA Einodahu $awobN walaA rawobN","text_ar":"مَا عِنْدَهُ شَوْبٌ وَلَا رَوْبٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He has not broth nor milk."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K: but in the latter,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA lahu","text_ar":"مَا لَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$awobN","text_ar":"شَوْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A piece of dough."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b4-  And [the pl.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$owaAbN","text_ar":"اَشْوَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A medley,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mixed multitude, of sundry sorts:"},{"kind":"text","text":"a less particular term than"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^awobaA$N","text_ar":"اَوْبَاشٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which signifies a medley, or mixed multitude, of the low, or lower, or lowest, sort: (TA, from a trad.:) accord. to El-Jawáleekee, it is an arabicized word, from the Pers."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=$uwbN","text_ar":"ا=شُوبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"w$b","text_ar":"وشب"},{"kind":"text","text":".)"}],"source_refs":["TA","S","K","IAar"]},{"entry_id":"n23258","headword_ar":"شُوبٌ","root":"$wb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uwbFA","text_ar":"شُوبًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the next preceding paragraph."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}